<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka sapum leh ka hinna hi,
 Lal Isu kawmah ka pie tai;
 Buona bangmah lau ta puong ka,
 Ka neih cheng tawh ka kipumpiek (2)

[V2]
 2. Lal Isu mai hi hinna pen,
 Kumsawt Pa Chamna Lal ahi;
 Amah kawmah hinna A um,
 Gitloh ngawlna a pukte di'n (2)

[V3]
 3. Khawvel ah mihiem a um em?
 Mi thiengtho leh gitlohna bei;
 Mihing Chapa, Lal Isu mai,
 Gitloh, buokna neilo ahi. (2)

[V4]
 4. Khawvel neihzawh leh nawpna hi,
 Beimanna leh thepna ahi;
 Mahleh pielgal neihzawhna chuh,
 Kumsawt chan inle kang puona. (2)

[V5]
 5. Isu'n ka gitloh A tan tai,
 Suok apatin ei puidawk tai;
 Ziebang bawlthei chu a um em?
 Gitloh suoka ei tatdawk chuh. (2)</lyrics>
<title>MY SOULAND BODY</title>
<hymn_number>173</hymn_number>
</song>